::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You should become the supreme guardian.
:::::You should become the supreme guardian.
:::::{{A|VO chapter1 4 bronya 230.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' You mean...
:::::{{A|VO chapter1 4 bronya 231.ogg}} '''Bronya:''' ...What was I thinking!? No... I shouldn't... That was a diabolical thought!
